address2: Fifth Floor Al Sadd-Suhaim Bin Hamad Street
longBusinessSummary: Widam Food Company Q.P.S.C. engages in the production, import, and trade of livestock, meat, and feed products in Qatar and Sudan. The company is also involved in the slaughtering of sheep and cattle; supply of fresh meat and related products; and sale of live and frozen meat. It serves hospitals, hotels, airlines, restaurants, catering companies, hypermarkets, and small butcheries. The company was formerly known as Qatar Company for Meat and Livestock Trading (MAWASHI) Q.S.C. and changed its name to Widam Food Company Q.P.S.C. in March 2013. Widam Food Company Q.P.S.C. was incorporated in 2003 and is based in Doha, Qatar.
